{"tid":657020,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔識先成除後加減既入一入來","createTime":"2018-05-07T17:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T17:41:31.000Z","uid":182244,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6e5d644a9c4975df1577d24439b1ae2fea0578","tid":657020,"uid":182244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:41:31.000Z","msg":"見上次出左世上第一部連登牌計數機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/642237/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/642237/1</a><br />\n再開多個post講講cal 機。唔係講笑，見過好多中學生，唔識用普通cal機計先乘除後加減數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次要講旣係普通計數機旣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信各位有讀個account旣巴絲都知道呢個掣點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道有d人唔識，見網上又無咩人教，有既又無show步驟，所以開個post,等各位唔識旣巴絲，就算無左部sci-cal，都可以輕鬆計到乘除。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上，呢三個掣都係普通cal機既memory。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 將數值Add至memory中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 從memory中減去數值<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 顯示memory中的數值<br />\nDouble click<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 清除記憶體<br />\n<br />\n就咁講可能有d抽象，宜家實戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6 x 3 - 7 x 4 + 2 x 6<br />\n正確答案係2，但如果順序按機，會出左276<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正確計法應該係咁（先步驟，後解釋）<br />\n1. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n清除返上次計數遺留下既記憶，等記憶歸零，習慣上要咁按<br />\n2.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6x3不解釋，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係將18，加入記憶體<br />\n3.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7x4不解釋，但今次我地要減返28，換句話我地亦要從memory中減去28，所以今次要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同step 2 一樣，今次我地加2x6入記憶<br />\n5.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計曬後按<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />show 返記憶，亦即係答案，show返個2出來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時間再講下GT，F320A 等等旣掣點用"}]}